FBIS4-42098 "drweu104_j_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-104 Daily Report 27 May 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Government Passes Employment Package Government Passes Employment Package LD2705204794 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1652 GMT 27 May 94 LD2705204794 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Text] The Council of Ministers has passed a major package of economic decrees which renews a number of expiring decrees, as well as introduces new regulations designed to streamline job placement, make direct recruitment easier, and provide fresh funds for Law 44, dealing with youth employment. The announcement was made by Labor Minister Mastella. He announced that a total of 500 billion lire has been earmarked for Law 44, 100 billion lire in 1994, and 200 billion each in the years 1995 and 1996.
